  "text": "Note that we have not used any special properties of graphic matroids. The algorithm from Calinescu et al. [CITATION_1] works for general matroids accessible through oracle calls. So we can apply our technique to more general problems where the objective is to minimize a function like Equation (21) subject to base matroid constraints.",
